<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>sicompass — Third-Party Licenses</title>
<style>
body { font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 760px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; }
h1 { font-size: 1.4rem; }
.intro { color: #444; }
.dep { border-top: 1px solid #ccc; padding-top: 1rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
.dep h2 { font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; }
.meta { color: #666; font-size: 0.85rem; }
pre { background: #f6f6f6; padding: 0.75rem; overflow-x: auto; font-size: 0.8rem; white-space: pre-wrap; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Third-Party Licenses</h1>
<p class="intro">
sicompass incorporates the following third-party software. Each component is
distributed under its own license, reproduced below. This notice is provided
to satisfy the attribution requirements of those licenses and applies to both
the commercial and GPLv3 distributions of sicompass.
</p>
<p class="intro">
Some components are licensed under the Mozilla Public License 2.0
(<code>cssparser</code>, <code>cssparser-macros</code>, <code>dtoa-short</code>,
<code>nucleo-matcher</code>, <code>selectors</code>). The MPL requires that the
source of those files be made available to recipients. sicompass uses these
crates unmodified, and their complete source is published at
<code>https://crates.io/crates/&lt;name&gt;</code> (for example,
<a href="https://crates.io/crates/selectors">https://crates.io/crates/selectors</a>).
The same applies to every other component listed here. This satisfies the MPL
source-availability requirement for both the commercial and GPLv3 distributions.
</p>

{{#each licenses}}
<div class="dep">
<h2>{{name}}</h2>
<p class="meta">Used by: {{#each used_by}}{{crate.name}} {{crate.version}}{{#unless @last}}, {{/unless}}{{/each}}</p>
<pre>{{text}}</pre>
</div>
{{/each}}

</body>
</html>
